{"title":"Life and Death and Knowledge","author":{"name":"Gabriel Gadfly"},"publishDate":"2011-10-13","lines":[{"line":"I.","stanza":1,"number":1},{"line":"You have only these hours and days.","stanza":1,"number":2},{"line":"II.","stanza":2,"number":3},{"line":"When you accept them,","stanza":2,"number":4},{"line":"you have no need of","stanza":2,"number":5},{"line":"afterlives or priorlives.","stanza":2,"number":6},{"line":"You have the single empty box","stanza":2,"number":7},{"line":"of a life and all the universe","stanza":2,"number":8},{"line":"to fill it with.","stanza":2,"number":9},{"line":"III.","stanza":3,"number":10},{"line":"Live like this: there is an end to you.","stanza":3,"number":11},{"line":"Don’t fear it. Don’t wallow.","stanza":3,"number":12},{"line":"Flowers wilt. Rivers dry up.","stanza":3,"number":13},{"line":"Even the stars extinguish themselves.","stanza":3,"number":14},{"line":"Have your time and then let it go.","stanza":3,"number":15},{"line":"IV.","stanza":4,"number":16},{"line":"Do not shy from your ending","stanza":4,"number":17},{"line":"with mad horse eyes.","stanza":4,"number":18},{"line":"V.","stanza":5,"number":19},{"line":"Allow the box of your life,","stanza":5,"number":20},{"line":"when you have filled it,","stanza":5,"number":21},{"line":"to have its spaces.","stanza":5,"number":22},{"line":"Resist the temptation","stanza":5,"number":23},{"line":"to stuff the gaps with gods","stanza":5,"number":24},{"line":"who do not know you.","stanza":5,"number":25},{"line":"VI.","stanza":6,"number":26},{"line":"Pull Uncertainty into your arms","stanza":6,"number":27},{"line":"and kiss her on the lips:","stanza":6,"number":28},{"line":"too many neglect her,","stanza":6,"number":29},{"line":"but she is an eager lover,","stanza":6,"number":30},{"line":"and desires only your attention.","stanza":6,"number":31},{"line":"Let her teach you how to say","stanza":6,"number":32},{"line":"“I don’t know, and that is beautiful.”","stanza":6,"number":33},{"line":"VII.","stanza":7,"number":34},{"line":"You have only these minutes and years.","stanza":7,"number":35}]}